Play Chorus again & end song on harmonics

 Key:
 h  hammer-on
 p  pull-off
 /  slide up
 \  slide down
  harmonic notes
 NH natural harmonic (lightly touch string above that fret)
 b  string bend
 ~  vibrato (affect pitch of note by shaking your fret hand/finger)